<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-28-1006 </DOCNO><TEXT>The paper treats the special relationship between the high-efficiencyparticulate air filter and the nuclear energy program. Discussed arethe following topics: initial development of paper-made filtration medium,original high-efficiency filter and its combustibility, high-temperaturehigh-efficiency filter, fire-resistant design, chemical corrosion inairstreams, water repellency of filter medium, sealants, gasketing, noveldesigns for increased capacity, filter testing, HEPA acronym, and government-industrycommittee for filter improvements.</TEXT></DOC>